data.description: This 6 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 living, and 2 dining home in Yowell Ranch features a spacious layout perfect for a large family or those who need plenty of space. The three-car garage provides ample parking and storage options. The property is located in Yowell Ranch neighborhood, offering a convenient and family-friendly community. With six bedrooms, there's plenty of room for everyone to have their own space, and the three bathrooms ensure comfort and convenience for all residents. It also features a big backyard with no bach neighbors. Yowell Ranch has a community swimming pool, walking trails, a dog park, and a community center.
